## AI Customer Support Ticket Router

### What it does
Receives support tickets via webhook, classifies them as billing/technical/general 
using Groq AI, routes each to a separate Google Sheet, and sends real-time 
Telegram alerts for every new ticket.

### Workflow
Webhook → Groq AI → Code Node → IF (billing?) → Google Sheets + Telegram
                                → IF (technical?) → Google Sheets + Telegram
                                                  → Google Sheets + Telegram

### How to use
1. Import workflow.json into your n8n instance
2. Add your Groq API key in the HTTP Request node
3. Create 3 Google Sheets: Billing Tickets, Technical Tickets, General Tickets
4. Add your Telegram bot token and chat ID
5. Test with Postman — POST to your webhook URL

